	<Title>
		Control your portions, control your weight
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Supersized portions can lead to supersized waists. Follow these tips before you dig into your next meal: 1. Read nutrition labels to determine accurate serving sizes. 2. Drink sparkling water or diet soda instead of regular soft drinks. 3. Don&apos;t force yourself to clean your plate. It&apos;s OK to stop when you&apos;re full.&lt;/p&gt;
